https://i.imgur.com/9DvT4JH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>A fine new year to the lot of you.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DMPJ7IB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ChaosPersonified]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Living by yourself can be lonely</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/bm2dYfC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yba8wY3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/bm2dYfC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SkyPigeon123]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Crimeception.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fftz2s2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gOPik8g.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fftz2s2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NoCapes]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Instructions for 2025</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/U1uVijm</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/aiZzSXx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/U1uVijm</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Nothing reminds you of success than recalling a past cringe</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/HykBHWs</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/x2sWtgx.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/HykBHWs</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MayMyEnemiesLiveLong]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Balancing fisherman tutorial</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YNnsTh1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/FZmSaRc.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Made a few of these for fishing friends. You could adapt to other designs.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/THrGFtf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>4d 1-1/4” finish nails. 8d 2-1/2” framing nail. 1/4” round stock, 1/8x1/2 flat bar - 1” long. Not pictured, 11” length of wire and 1-1/2” long piece of flat bar to make the fish.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BTq1DZt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cut two of the finish nails to 1” length. Cut the framing nail head and point off.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hi2h8rU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Bend the 1” cut nails as shown. Layout against the flat bar. I put them both in a vise and hammer them over at the same time so they’re consistent.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DiV09iK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Weld the “hands” together.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/rnqPb1S.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Put a small bend in the elbows.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8005leE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Set the arms at the angle you like and weld to body.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WkCpT6N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Set the legs and weld into place.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SvNLVki.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>For the head, round it as desired before cutting. Easier to hold that way.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OkaVJYK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cut it off to whatever length you like.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Au4SJmE.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I welded a bead on the bottom of the head to make a neck. You don’t have to.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YQ3SW08.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe shoulda welded the head before the arms. I welded from the back.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/M7uqdXK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/YWgnOoJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Weld the fishing rod as shown. Don’t worry too much about the angle. Everything can be bent to adjust later.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/i9Rht1j.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cut a piece of wire about 11” long.  Bend a curve in it around a 4” radius.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ClHer6n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Weld the wire to the rod at about a right angle.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eUVckvn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I cut the fish out of the same flat bar, 1-1/2” long. After cutting I polished it up with a flapper wheel. I used a sanding disc on the dremel to give the sorta fish scale design.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ydIQdbH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lay it flat and weld the fish to the wire.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/qjl3jw2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I heated it with a torch to get a nice blue/purple oxide. While it’s hot, I apply some oil to help prevent rust.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ovy2jWn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>More blue oxide.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YNnsTh1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[bloomautomatic]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Terry knows his strengths, and he knows where to apply them best</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DDZZ2ve</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Kj4FKuG.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DDZZ2ve</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SnowglobeOfDoom]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Let's start the year right mu dudes</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Nmm8VzM</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/S0uByLb.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gLsykRW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/swVjxDO.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Yeah I'm bringing it back, join me won't you?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Nmm8VzM</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[JinButOnHisPhone]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>By Your Smallest Acts of Kindness...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DGyJ8IP</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/B7Anr0n.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>( ◕‿◕)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DGyJ8IP</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[FrostyLady]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Oh honey, it will be messy.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IWQG6pd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/iIL3KKC.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IWQG6pd</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[countervail247365]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>My neighborhood right now</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MdcRFNo</lin